<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV65">
<l>niṟpatummor veṟpakatti ruppumviṇki ṭappatum</l>
<l>naṟperunti raikkaṭaluḷ nāṉilāta muṉṉelā</l>
<l>maṟputaṉa ṉantacayaṉa ṉātipūtaṉ mātavaṉ</l>
<l>niṟpatummi ruppatuṅki ṭappatumeṉ ṉeñcuḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Wonderful [Lord], Anantaśāyin, the Primeval Being, Mādhava: [His]</l>
<l>Standing on a matchless hill, sitting in Heaven, and lying on a big, good ocean</l>
<l>Was all before, when I was not [there].</l>
<l>[Now His] standing, sitting, and lying down are inside my heart!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
